      "content": "i dont see the point in talking to people. they just dont get it. they tell me \"it gets better\" or \"at least you had good years with him\" and it just makes me feel more alone. it's like there's this massive, suffocating weight on my chest and i just want it to stop. i just want to be able to sleep and not wake up to this emptiness every single day.",
