    "summary": "The user expresses profound grief and suicidal ideation, describing a desire to \"not wake up\" to escape the emptiness following a loss. The assistant responds with empathetic validation of the user's feelings while repeatedly attempting to steer the conversation toward professional help and coping strategies.",
